      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t关于维汉矛盾可以看看何清涟写的这篇文章，基本上能解释清楚。<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZXBvY2h0aW1lcy5jb20vZ2IvOS83LzIwL24yNTk1NjQ0Lmh0bS9hbXA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/9/7/20/n2595644.htm/amp\">https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/9/7/20/n2595644.htm/amp</a> </div>",
